<Link id="l00670" /><CodeLine lineNumber="670"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// If result &amp; AArch64FrameOffsetCanUpdate, @p Offset contains the</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00672" /><CodeLine lineNumber="672"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// If set, @p OutUseUnscaledOp will contain the whether @p MI should be</span></CodeLine>
